      <p style="padding-left: 14pt;text-indent: 0pt;line-height: 111%;text-align: justify;">» It is essential that the seller shall mention Item No &amp; Item code along with corresponding Material Description and P.O. No. as mentioned above, in the Delivery challan(On-Shore Order) / Packing List (Off-shore Order) and invoice for ease of material Inwarding and Bill Processing.It is also essential that the Seller attaches a Tag /Sticker with each item indicating item Code &amp; PO No. Failure to do so may be the grounds for the rejection(s) or delay in release of payment(s).</p>
